  • java.lang.Object
    • com.atakmap.android.cot.detail.CotDetailHandler
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AddressDetailHandler, BullseyeDetailHandler, EmergencyDetailHandler, ForceXDetailHandler, GeoFenceDetailHandler, MarkerIncludedRouteDetailHandler, MetaDetailHandler, PrecisionLocationHandler, RouteDetailHandler, RouteRequiredWayPointHandler, SensorDetailHandler, ShapeDetailHandler, ShapeMsdDetailHandler, SPIDetailHandler, TacticalOverlayDetailHandler, TakVersionDetailHandler, VehicleModelDetailHandler, VideoDetailHandler
    public abstract class CotDetailHandler
extends java.lang.Object
    Converts map item meta data to CoT details and vice versa These methods should be called when converting to and from CoT for a specific detail (usually supplied by map item metadata)
